### INSTRUÇÕES:
### 1. Execute o teste 2 (Login com ADMIN)
### 2. Copie o token JWT do response
### 3. Cole o token aqui: @JWT_TOKEN = SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
### 4. Depois execute os demais testes

### 0. PRIMEIRO: Criar usuário ADMIN
POST {{host}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "AdminSenha@123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 1. Cadastro de novo usuário
POST {{host}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao3@example.com",
  "password": "Senha@123",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 2. SEGUNDO: Login com ADMIN (Executar este para gerar o token JWT)
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "AdminSenha@123"
}

### 2. SEGUNDO: Login com USER
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao3@example.com",
  "password": "Senha@123"
}

### 3. Obter dados do usuário autenticado (GET /users/me)
GET {{host}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### 4. Listar todos os usuários (Requer role ADMIN)
GET {{host}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### 5. Obter usuário por ID
GET {{host}}/users/3
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### 6. Atualizar usuário (PATCH /users/{id})
PATCH {{host}}/users/4
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "name": "João Silva Atualizado",
  "email": "joao.novo@example.com",
  "password": "NovaSenha@123"
}

### 8. Criar segundo usuário para testes
POST {{host}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Santos",
  "email": "maria@example.com",
  "password": "Senha@456",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 9. Criar usuário com role ENG
POST {{host}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Carlos Engineer",
  "email": "carlos@example.com",
  "password": "Senha@789",
  "role": "ENG"
}


### Projects CRUD tests (use same @JWT_TOKEN)
# Create project
POST {{host}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Obra de Teste",
  "address": "Rua das Flores, 100",
  "projectType": "RESIDENTIAL",
  "category": "HOUSE",
  "landArea": 250.00,
  "builtArea": 180.00,
  "status": "PLANNING",
  "plannedStartDate": "2026-06-01",
  "plannedEndDate": "2026-12-01"
}

### List projects
GET {{host}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### Get project by id (replace 1 with created id)
GET {{host}}/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### Update project (PATCH)
PATCH {{host}}/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "address": "Av. Atualizada, 200",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### Delete project
DELETE {{host}}/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### Unauthenticated request (should return 401)
GET {{host}}/projects
